title: Change Is In The Air, Feel Today
posting_body: ["Mosaic Apartments provide all of the modern amenities you've been waiting for.", 'Once inside your brand-new apartment home you’ll enjoy the best in sophisticated apartment finishes where no detail has been overlooked.', 'Discover an elevated lifestyle with the opportunity for fine living and an unsurpassed location at a great value.', 'Come in and Tour Your New Home Today!!', 'We are open 7 days a week 9:00 AM- 6:00 PM', 'Mosaic Apartments (CA)', '500 Race Street', 'San Jose, CA 95126', '<URL>', 'Community Amenities', 'Easy Access to Light Rail •', 'We Love Pets!', '* •', 'Complimentary Fitness Classes • Fitness Center • Bike Storage •', 'Professional On-Site Management • Reserved Underground Parking* • Executive Business Center • Resident Lounge • Resort-Inspired Pool •', 'Relaxing Spa • Outdoor Seating Area • Online Rental Payments • Smoke-Free Community • Theater Rental •', 'Wi Fi Available • Car Charging Station', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Complete Stainless-Steel Appliance Package • Custom Wood-Style Flooring* • Elevators and Handicap Accessible Units • Energy Star Appliances • Washer/Dryer • Heating • Granite Countertops Throughout • Wood Cabinetry', '*Restrictions Apply.']
